relationships.description: The `yao start` command is used to start the application server in Yao.
Development mode in Yao watches changes to DSL and Process files and reloads the server.
The `yao run` command is used to run a process in Yao.
Visual Studio Code is recommended for developing Yao applications.
The `.yao` file type should be set to `jsonc` in Visual Studio Code for syntax highlighting and auto-completion.
The 'Building Your Application' documentation is related to building applications with Yao.
